63.0	Tropic_Thunder	Tropic Thunder	Tropic Thunder is a 2008 American action comedy film written, produced, and directed by Ben Stiller, and starring Stiller, Robert Downey, Jr., and Jack Black. The main plot revolves around a group of prima donna actors who are making their fictional Vietnam War film. When their frustrated writer and director decide to drop them in the middle of a jungle, they are forced to rely on their acting skills in order to survive the real action and danger. Also written by Justin Theroux and Etan Cohen, the film was produced by Red Hour Films and distributed by DreamWorks Pictures through Paramount Pictures.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d6/Tropic_thunder_ver3.jpg/220px-Tropic_thunder_ver3.jpg
